    CHANGELOG (v2.0 — Major Overhaul):

    ── ARCHITECTURE ────────────────────────────────────────
    • Maid cleanup system — every connection tracked; zero leaks on Destroy()
    • Per-window DragType (was module-level → broke 2+ windows)
    • StoredInfo is now per-window (was module-level → tab collisions fixed)
    • Native Color3:Lerp replaces manual LerpColor implementation

    ── PERFORMANCE ─────────────────────────────────────────
    • Slider: event-driven via RunService.Heartbeat (removes CPU polling loop)
    • Touch slider: uses InputObject.Position directly (no Player.Mouse fallback)
    • Theme engine: same O(n) sweep but all new components registered in rules

    ── BUG FIXES ───────────────────────────────────────────
    • Minimize: now sets Opened=false so keybind can re-open
    • Dropdown: post-close Destroy delay 2 s → 0.3 s
    • Input: duplicate FocusLost connection removed
    • Hover base color re-captured correctly per call (not shared upvalue)
    • Keybind: Listening guard prevents double-capture on rapid click

    ── COMPONENT RETURN OBJECTS ────────────────────────────
    All Add* now return a control table:
      Toggle:Set(bool)      / Toggle:Get()      / Toggle:OnChanged(fn)
      Slider:Set(n)         / Slider:Get()      / Slider:OnChanged(fn)
      Input:Set(str)        / Input:Get()
      Dropdown:Set(value)   / Dropdown:Get()
      Keybind:Set(keycode)  / Keybind:Get()     / Keybind:OnChanged(fn)
      ColorPicker:Set(c3)   / ColorPicker:Get()
      ProgressBar:Set(0–1)  / ProgressBar:Get()
      Paragraph:SetTitle(s) / Paragraph:SetDescription(s)
      Label:Set(str)        / Label:Get()

    ── NEW COMPONENTS ──────────────────────────────────────
    • AddColorPicker()    — HSV wheel + hex input (UIGradient, no assets)
    • AddMultiDropdown()  — multi-select with ✓ indicators
    • AddProgressBar()    — animated read-only fill bar
    • AddLabel()          — lightweight single-line text element
    • AddDivider()        — horizontal separator line

    ── WINDOW API ──────────────────────────────────────────
    • Window:Destroy()            — full teardown, all connections severed
    • Window:SetVisible(bool)     — programmatic show/hide
    • Window:OnThemeChanged(fn)   — register callback on theme switch

    ── NOTIFICATIONS ───────────────────────────────────────
    • Proper vertical stacking — multiple toasts stack upward

    ── MOBILE ──────────────────────────────────────────────
    • Swipe left/right gesture on the window to navigate tabs
    • Larger touch targets maintained (IsMobile detection)
    • Touch slider uses actual touch position

]]


